title: Dow's (DOW) Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates in Q3
text: Dow (DOW) topped earnings and sales estimates in Q3 despite headwinds from energy cost inflation and lower demand in EMEAI.

title: Dow Inc. (DOW) Beats Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
text: Dow Inc. (DOW) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 7.77% and 6.91%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2022. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

title: The 10 Best Dow Jones Stocks to Buy Before the Market Recovers
text: On Thursday, Wedbush analyst Dan Ives reiterated his $215 target price for Salesforce (NYSE: CRM ), re-crowning the software firm as the Dow Jones stock with the highest implied upside. For many first-time investors, these target prices are often irresistible.
